videoSnippet.title: DrNykterstein (Magnus Carlsen) Plays King's Gambit || Lichess Titled Arena
videoSnippet.description:
Link to tournament and game https://lichess.org/iRBVCohQ#37
https://lichess.org/tournament/jul19lta

Download agadmator chess clock here https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.agadmator.chessclock&fbclid=IwAR3b_sRch6nsuW59-bWoirVDMMJ8V5jexZdUB0bsxQrc0Q8imvkBtqkHUXQ&rdid=com.agadmator.chessclock

Follow me on Instagram for extra content https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Magnus Carlsen vs Daniel Naroditsky
Lichess Titled Arena (2019), Jul-19 
King's Gambit (C30)

1. e4 e5 2. f4 Nc6 3. Nc3 exf4 4. d4 Qh4+ 5. Ke2 b6 6. a4 Nf6 7. Nf3 Ba6+ 8. Nb5 Qh5 9. e5 Ne4 10. Bxf4 O-O-O 11. Ke3 d6 12. Nxa7+ Nxa7 13. Bxa6+ Kb8 14. Kxe4 dxe5 15. Nxe5 Qh4 16. Qf3 Bc5 17. c3 Rhe8 18. Kd3 c6 {forced} 19. Nxc6+ Ka8 20. Na5+ Nc6 21. Qxc6+ Ka7 22. Qb7#
